    "fr": "Inspirer l’apprentissage par l’espace",
    "status": "translated"
  },
  {
    "id": "educators § inspiring-learning-through-space § p1",
    "section": "inspiring-learning-through-space",
    "tag": "p",
    "en": "Out of This World 25 offers educators new ways to connect <strong>science, history, innovation, and storytelling</strong> in the classroom.",
    "fr": "Out of This World 25 offre aux éducateurs de nouvelles façons de relier <strong>la science, l’histoire, l’innovation et la narration</strong> en salle de classe.",
    "status": "translated"
  },
  {
    "id": "educators § inspiring-learning-through-space § p2",
    "section": "inspiring-learning-through-space",
    "tag": "p",
    "en": "Through the story of <strong>Chris Hadfield’s 2001 mission</strong>, Canada’s role aboard the <strong>International Space Station</strong>, and the historic <strong>Artemis II mission</strong>, OOTW25 helps students explore how curiosity, teamwork, and discovery shape our understanding of the world and beyond.",
    "fr": "Grâce à l’histoire de la <strong>mission de Chris Hadfield en 2001</strong>, du rôle du Canada à bord de la <strong>Station spatiale internationale</strong> et de la <strong>mission historique Artemis II</strong>, OOTW25 aide les élèves à explorer comment la curiosité, le travail d’équipe et la découverte façonnent notre compréhension du monde et au-delà.",
    "status": "translated"
  },
  {
    "id": "educators § inspiring-learning-through-space § p3",
    "section": "inspiring-learning-through-space",
    "tag": "p",
    "en": "Developed in collaboration with <strong>McMaster Children and Youth University (MCYU)</strong> and project partners across Canada, these resources are designed to support meaningful, interdisciplinary learning.",
    "fr": "Élaborées en collaboration avec la <strong>McMaster Children and Youth University (MCYU)</strong> et des partenaires du projet partout au Canada, ces ressources sont conçues pour soutenir un apprentissage interdisciplinaire significatif.",
    "status": "translated"
  },
  {
    "id": "educators § teaching-space-means-teaching-curiosity- § h21",
    "section": "teaching-space-means-teaching-curiosity-",
    "tag": "h2",
    "en": "Teaching space means teaching curiosity, discovery, and possibility.",
    "fr": "Enseigner l’espace, c’est enseigner la curiosité, la découverte et les possibilités.",
    "status": "translated"
  },
  {
