  {
    "id": "educators § through-out-of-this-world-25-educators-c § h21",
    "section": "through-out-of-this-world-25-educators-c",
    "tag": "h2",
    "en": "Through Out of This World 25, educators can help students connect Canada’s achievements in space with the possibilities of tomorrow.\nCuriosity in the classroom can inspire the explorers of the future.",
    "fr": "Grâce à Out of This World 25, les éducateurs peuvent aider les élèves à relier les réussites du Canada dans l’espace aux possibilités de demain.\nLa curiosité en salle de classe peut inspirer les explorateurs de demain.",
    "status": "translated"
  },
  {
    "id": "educators § through-out-of-this-world-25-educators-c § p1",
